privacy_policy:
U-{name} wakhe uhlelo lokusebenza lwe-iJot njengohlelo lokusebenza lwamahhala. Le SERVICE ihlinzekwa ngu-{name} mahhala futhi ihloselwe ukusetshenziswa njengoba injalo.

Lokhu okokwazisa abasebenzisi mayelana nezinqubomgomo zami ngokuqoqwa, ukusetshenziswa, nokudalulwa Kolwazi Lomuntu Siqu uma umuntu enquma ukusebenzisa Isevisi yami.

Uma ukhetha ukusebenzisa Isevisi yami, lapho-ke uyavumelana nokuqoqwa nokusetshenziswa kolwazi ngokuhlobene nale nqubomgomo. Ngeke ngisebenzise noma ngabelane ngolwazi lwakho nanoma ubani ngaphandle kokuthi kuchazwe kule Nqubomgomo Yobumfihlo.


**Ukuqoqwa nokusetshenziswa kolwazi**

Ukuze uthole ulwazi olungcono, ngenkathi usebenzisa Isevisi yethu, ngingase ngidinge ukuthi usinikeze ulwazi oluthile olungahlonza umuntu siqu, oluhlanganisa kodwa olungagcini nje ngegama lomsebenzisi ne-imeyili. Ulwazi engilucelayo luzogcinwa kudivayisi yakho futhi aluqoqwa yimi nganoma iyiphi indlela.

Uhlelo lokusebenza alusebenzisi amasevisi ezinkampani zangaphandle ezingase ziqoqe ulwazi olusetshenziselwa ukukuhlonza.

Isixhumanisi esiya kunqubomgomo yobumfihlo yabahlinzeki besevisi abavela eceleni abasetshenziswa uhlelo lokusebenza

* [Izinkonzo ze-Google Play](https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/)

* [I-Google Analytics ye-Firebase](https://firebase.google.com/policies/analytics)


**Idatha Yelogi**

Ngifuna ukukwazisa ukuthi noma nini uma usebenzisa Isevisi yami, esimweni sephutha kuhlelo lokusebenza ngiqoqa idatha nolwazi (ngemikhiqizo yezinkampani zangaphandle) kufoni yakho ebizwa ngokuthi Idatha Yelogi. Le datha yelogi ingase ihlanganise ulwazi olufana nekheli ledivayisi yakho Yephrothokholi Ye-inthanethi (“IP”), igama ledivayisi, inguqulo yesistimu yokusebenza, ukumiswa kohlelo lokusebenza lapho ngisebenzisa Isevisi yami, isikhathi nosuku lokusebenzisa kwakho Isevisi, nezinye izibalo. .


**Abahlinzeki Besevisi**

Ngingase ngiqashe izinkampani zangaphandle kanye nabantu ngabanye ngenxa yalezi zizathu ezilandelayo:

* Ukwenza lula Inkonzo yethu;

* Ukuhlinzeka Ngesevisi esikhundleni sethu;

* Ukwenza izinsizakalo eziphathelene nesevisi; noma

* Ukusisiza ekuhlaziyeni ukuthi Isevisi yethu isetshenziswa kanjani.

Ngifuna ukwazisa abasebenzisi bale Nsizakalo ukuthi lezi zinkampani zangaphandle ziyakwazi ukufinyelela Ulwazi Lwakho Lomuntu Siqu. Isizathu wukwenza imisebenzi abanikezwe yona egameni lethu. Nokho, banesibopho sokungadaluli noma basebenzise ulwazi nganoma iyiphi enye injongo.


**Ezokuphepha**

Ngiyakwazisa ukwethemba kwakho ekusinikezeni Ulwazi Lwakho Lomuntu Siqu, ngaleyo ndlela silwela ukusebenzisa izindlela ezamukelekayo ezithengiswayo zokuluvikela. Kodwa khumbula ukuthi ayikho indlela yokudlulisela nge-inthanethi, noma indlela yokugcina i-electronic evikelekile futhi ithembekile ngo-100%, futhi angikwazi ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha kwayo okuphelele.


**Izinguquko Kule Nqubomgomo Yobumfihlo**

Ngingahle ngibuyekeze Inqubomgomo yethu Yobumfihlo ngezikhathi ezithile. Ngakho-ke, uyalulekwa ukuthi ubuyekeze leli khasi ngezikhathi ezithile nganoma yiziphi izinguquko. Ngizokwazisa nganoma yiziphi izinguquko ngokuthumela Inqubomgomo Yobumfihlo entsha kuleli khasi.
